# Tauri requires icon files at the paths listed in tauri.conf.json:
#
#   icons/32x32.png
#   icons/128x128.png
#   icons/128x128@2x.png
#   icons/icon.icns
#   icons/icon.ico
#
# Generate them once with:
#
#   pnpm tauri icon path/to/source.png
#
# Until then, `tauri build` will fail. `tauri dev` may still run depending on
# the platform. Drop a 1024x1024 PNG into the repo root and run the command above.
